25
00:01:43,599 --> 00:01:49,000
Now another part that we have added to JDK is an ability to execute other languages,

26
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:54,599
that are not traditionally JVM languages on top of the JVM and within Java applications.

27
00:01:54,599 --> 00:01:58,320
So one thing you can do with GraalVM is you can extend your Java application with languages

28
00:01:58,320 --> 00:02:03,959
