00:27:39,859 --> 00:27:41,899
So let's say, oh, by the way, did you

569
00:27:41,899 --> 00:27:43,619
know that you can do this?

570
00:27:43,619 --> 00:27:45,940
Well, it would have been installed, but in my case,

