00:27:45,940 --> 00:27:47,380
less because I already have it.

572
00:27:47,380 --> 00:27:48,780
Oh, wrong.

573
00:27:48,780 --> 00:27:51,340
Visual VM.

574
00:27:51,340 --> 00:27:53,419
So you can install Visual VM as SDK man,

575
00:27:53,419 --> 00:27:55,459
and you can manage it along with your JDKs.

576
00:27:55,459 --> 00:27:56,940
I think this is pretty cool.

577
00:27:56,940 --> 00:27:58,579
So I have my Visual VM.

578
00:27:58,579 --> 00:28:00,459
Let's get it started.

