00:28:02,540 --> 00:28:04,940
that you can actually monitor in Visual VM.

581
00:28:04,940 --> 00:28:07,579
So I have the same app, or rather very similar,

582
00:28:07,579 --> 00:28:09,179
that I was showing to you before.

