586
00:28:14,619 --> 00:28:17,780
Demo Central.

587
00:28:17,780 --> 00:28:21,780
Native Spring Boot SBOM.

588
00:28:21,780 --> 00:28:24,699
And I need my executable.

589
00:28:24,699 --> 00:28:27,940
So this is, again, a native Spring application that runs.

590
00:28:27,940 --> 00:28:32,019
And when we go here, it returns hello.

