602
00:28:56,459 --> 00:29:00,019
Now you can also include it as a class pass resource.

603
00:29:00,019 --> 00:29:01,660
And then it can be picked up from things

604
00:29:01,660 --> 00:29:03,420
like Spring Actuator.

605
00:29:03,420 --> 00:29:05,100
And I have exactly one minute, so I also

